entity.altText: MSTHOO Open Ear Headphones, 30H Playtime with Wireless Charging Case, Noise-Cancellation Mic for Clear Calls, IPX7 Waterproof Wireless Earbuds with Earhooks for Running, Walking and Workouts

featureBullets: 【Open Ear Clip Bluetooth Headphones, Secure and Comfortable Fit】Unlike traditional headphones, they feature a completely open design that rests gently on your ears without entering your ear canal. This reduces stress and the risk of hearing loss after extended wear. Additionally, the flexible silicone ear hooks and ergonomic design ensure a stable and comfortable fit, making them perfect for outdoor activities such as hiking and running.

【Powerful Stereo Sound & HIFI Clear Calls】These earphones feature dual 16MM vibrating diaphragm speaker drivers that maintain clear and balanced audio at any volume. The high compliance diaphragm delivers a rich bass range and enhances sound quality while minimizing distortion. Additionally, the built-in mic system is designed to prioritize your voice and reduce background noise, making calls easier and clearer to hear.

【Hear Your Surroundings & More security】The headphones allow you to immerse yourself in your music while remaining aware of your surroundings. Whether you're cycling, walking, running, working out, or driving, you can stay alert and aware of changes in your environment, making them a safe and practical choice for any activity. With these headphones, you can enjoy your music without compromising your safety or situational awareness.

【30 Hours Playtime with Charging Case】80 hours of standby time and 6 hours of playback on a single charge, or 30 hours of total playback with the charging case. The charging case supports wireless charging or USB-C fast charge. It is compact and easy to carry, making it ideal for daily use and travel.

【Low Latency Experience & IPX7 waterproof】Bluetooth earbuds feature the latest Bluetooth 5.2 technology, you can enjoy a low-latency listening experience with audio and video perfectly synced without any delay. With an IPX7 waterproof rating, these headphones can withstand sweat, rain, providing durable and reliable performance.
